Section 12: Extending Spring Boot
 Lecture 12.1 Know when to extend Spring Boot
 
* Why extend Spring Boot ?
  * Microservices mean lots of apps
  * What if your apps have their own conventions ?
    * Logging requirements
    * Security
    * Monitoring / Metrics
    * Databases

* Typical tasks
  * Curated dependencies
  * Custom auto-configuration
  * Extended Spring customizations
  
    